              <p className="mb-4">
                Pickleball is a paddle sport that combines elements of badminton, tennis, and table tennis. It's played
                both indoors and outdoors on a badminton-sized court with a slightly modified tennis net.
              </p>
              <p>
                Players use solid paddles made of wood or composite materials to hit a perforated polymer ball over the
